<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222100>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 15. Planaeschna maculifrons sp. nov., holotype male: (10) body in lateral view; (11) head in frontal view; (12) appendages in lateral view; (13) appendages in dorsal view; (14) vesica spermalis in lateral view; (15) vesica spermalisin ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222100/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222101>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 24. Planaeschna caudispina sp. nov., holotype male (16 – 17, 20 – 23) and paratype female (18 – 19, 24): (16) body in lateral view; (17) head in frontal view; (18) head in frontal view; (19) body in lateral view; (20) appendages in lateral view; (21) appendages in dorsal view; (22) vesica spermalisin lateral view; (23) vesica spermalisin ventral view; (24) ovipositor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

